    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="一、having"><a href="#一、having" class="headerlink" title="一、having"></a>一、having</h1><h2 id="1、having子句语法"><a href="#1、having子句语法" class="headerlink" title="1、having子句语法"></a>1、having子句语法</h2><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span> column1, column2, ... </span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">FROM</span> <span class="keyword">table</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">GROUP</span> <span class="keyword">BY</span> column1, column2, ...</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">HAVING</span> <span class="keyword">condition</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">&lt;</span><span class="operator">!</span><span class="comment">-- more --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">其中，<span class="keyword">SELECT</span>语句表示要查询的列，<span class="keyword">FROM</span>子句表示要查询的表，<span class="keyword">GROUP</span> <span class="keyword">BY</span>子句表示要对查询结果进行分组的列，<span class="keyword">HAVING</span>子句表示要对分组后的结果进行过滤的条件。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">## <span class="number">2</span>、注意事项</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">HAVING</span>子句有一些事项需要注意：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">（<span class="number">1</span>）分组列必须在<span class="keyword">SELECT</span>语句中出现：使用<span class="keyword">GROUP</span> <span class="keyword">BY</span>子句分组时，分组列必须在<span class="keyword">SELECT</span>语句中出现，否则会出现语法错误。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">（<span class="number">2</span>）聚合函数不能用于<span class="keyword">WHERE</span>子句：使用聚合函数时，不能在<span class="keyword">WHERE</span>子句中使用，因为<span class="keyword">WHERE</span>子句在聚合函数之前执行。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">（<span class="number">3</span>）<span class="keyword">HAVING</span>子句不能使用别名：<span class="keyword">HAVING</span>子句不能使用<span class="keyword">SELECT</span>语句中定义的别名，因为别名是在<span class="keyword">SELECT</span>语句之后计算的。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">（<span class="number">4</span>）<span class="keyword">HAVING</span>子句的条件必须是聚合函数：<span class="keyword">HAVING</span>子句的条件必须是聚合函数，而不能是普通的列名。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">（<span class="number">5</span>）<span class="keyword">HAVING</span>并不一定需要<span class="keyword">GROUP</span> <span class="keyword">BY</span>（可以参考使用场景：存在缺失的编号）。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">（<span class="number">6</span>）<span class="keyword">WHERE</span>面向的是行，<span class="keyword">HAVING</span>面向的是集合。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">（<span class="number">7</span>）过滤条件中有聚合函数时，则过滤条件必须声明在<span class="keyword">HAVING</span>中；如果没有，则建议写在<span class="keyword">WHERE</span>中，因为<span class="keyword">WHERE</span>的执行效率要高于<span class="keyword">HAVING</span>。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">（<span class="number">8</span>）分组操作会把分组的结果聚合成一条记录，而窗口函数（MySQL <span class="number">8.0</span>开始支持）是将结果置于每一条数据记录中。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 二、准备表数据</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">## <span class="number">1</span>、SeqTb</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">|</span> id   <span class="operator">|</span> name  <span class="operator">|</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">|</span> :<span class="comment">--- | :---- |</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">|</span> <span class="number">1</span>    <span class="operator">|</span> 迪克  <span class="operator">|</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">|</span> <span class="number">2</span>    <span class="operator">|</span> 安    <span class="operator">|</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">|</span> <span class="number">3</span>    <span class="operator">|</span> 莱露  <span class="operator">|</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">|</span> <span class="number">5</span>    <span class="operator">|</span> 卡    <span class="operator">|</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">|</span> <span class="number">6</span>    <span class="operator">|</span> 玛丽  <span class="operator">|</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">|</span> <span class="number">8</span>    <span class="operator">|</span> 本    <span class="operator">|</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">|</span> <span class="number">9</span>    <span class="operator">|</span> <span class="keyword">NULL</span>  <span class="operator">|</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">|</span> <span class="number">10</span>   <span class="operator">|</span> hi    <span class="operator">|</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">|</span> <span class="number">13</span>   <span class="operator">|</span> hello <span class="operator">|</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">## <span class="number">2</span>、Graduates</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">|</span> id   <span class="operator">|</span> name   <span class="operator">|</span> income <span class="operator">|</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">|</span> :<span class="comment">--- | :----- | :----- |</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">|</span> <span class="number">1</span>    <span class="operator">|</span> 桑普森 <span class="operator">|</span> <span class="number">40000</span>  <span class="operator">|</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">|</span> <span class="number">2</span>    <span class="operator">|</span> 迈克   <span class="operator">|</span> <span class="number">30000</span>  <span class="operator">|</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">|</span> <span class="number">3</span>    <span class="operator">|</span> 怀特   <span class="operator">|</span> <span class="number">20000</span>  <span class="operator">|</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">|</span> <span class="number">4</span>    <span class="operator">|</span> 阿诺德 <span class="operator">|</span> <span class="number">20000</span>  <span class="operator">|</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">|</span> <span class="number">5</span>    <span class="operator">|</span> 史密斯 <span class="operator">|</span> <span class="number">20000</span>  <span class="operator">|</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">|</span> <span class="number">6</span>    <span class="operator">|</span> 劳伦斯 <span class="operator">|</span> <span class="number">15000</span>  <span class="operator">|</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">|</span> <span class="number">7</span>    <span class="operator">|</span> 哈德逊 <span class="operator">|</span> <span class="number">15000</span>  <span class="operator">|</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">|</span> <span class="number">8</span>    <span class="operator">|</span> 肯特   <span class="operator">|</span> <span class="number">10000</span>  <span class="operator">|</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">|</span> <span class="number">9</span>    <span class="operator">|</span> 贝特   <span class="operator">|</span> <span class="number">10000</span>  <span class="operator">|</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">|</span> <span class="number">10</span>   <span class="operator">|</span> 斯科特 <span class="operator">|</span> <span class="number">10000</span>  <span class="operator">|</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 三、使用场景</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">## <span class="number">1</span>、存在缺失的编号（<span class="keyword">HAVING</span>不一定必须有<span class="keyword">GROUP</span> <span class="keyword">BY</span>）</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">```<span class="keyword">sql</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 如果有查询结果，说明存在缺失的编号</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="number">1</span> <span class="keyword">as</span> gap</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> SeqTb</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">having</span> <span class="built_in">count</span>(<span class="operator">*</span>) <span class="operator">&lt;&gt;</span> <span class="built_in">max</span>(id)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

